    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. Can you expand on the \"marketplace of ideas\" part? I want to argue that any attempt by the state to moderate content—even for things like preventing misinformation—is essentially a form of intellectual censorship that breaks the whole system. How would a philosopher like Mill frame that?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
